item.description:

I’ll be a server developer for you if you need one, I’ve been coding for 3 year’s and I can code up to 317+ so that means the highest revision.

Contact:
Skype: Tyrogasm
[/quote]

I honestly almost pissed myself from laughing so hard. The highest revision is well over 723. 317 is the first main revision, and the coding and packaging is much easier to understand. And if you’ve been ‘coding’ for three years you’d know that Java is programming, not coding. And also, I don’t see why anyone would want help from you, considering the fact that you can’t use the correct for of your/you’re.

Back to laughing.[/quote]

this…just this over and over again
